<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sharia DeFi - Coming Soon</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #162447);
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #fca311;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        ul {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0;
            list-style-type: none;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        li::before {
            content: "✔️";
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #fca311;
        }
        input[type="email"] {
            padding: 12px;
            width: 60%;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px 0 0 4px;
            outline: none;
        }
        button, .demo-btn {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
            background-color: #fca311;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        button:hover, .demo-btn:hover {
            background-color: #e59400;
        }
        .social {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .social a {
            color: #fca311;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .social a:hover {
            color: #e59400;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #aaa;
        }
        .demo-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Sharia DeFi</h1>
        <p>We are launching soon! Sharia DeFi is your trusted platform for Islamic-compliant decentralized finance.</p>
        <p>Our platform helps Islamic investors navigate DeFi with confidence through:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Real-time Shariah compliance scoring for DeFi protocols</li>
            <li>Expert verification by Islamic finance scholars</li>
            <li>Comprehensive interest-free and halal asset checks</li>
            <li>Transparent risk assessment and historical tracking</li>
        </ul>
        <form action="#">
            <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email to get updates" required>
            <button type="submit">Notify Me</button>
        </form>
        <a href="https://demo.shariadefi.app/" target="_blank" class="demo-btn">View Demo</a>
        <div class="social">
            <p>Follow us on X for updates:</p>
            <a href="https://x.com/defimmy" target="_blank">@defimmy</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2025 Sharia DeFi. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
